BRF S.A. Key Developments

BRF S.A. Appoints Alessandro Bonorino as Vice President of Human Resources, Effective August 21, 2017
Jul 18 17
BRF S.A. announced that Alessandro Bonorino, professional with over 20 years of experience in Human Resources, will assume as BRF's Vice President of Human Resources on August 21, 2017. His most recent position was at IBM, as Vice President of Human Resources for the Global Services Division.


BRF S.A., Board Meeting, Jun 29, 2017
Jul 11 17
BRF S.A., Board Meeting, Jun 29, 2017, at 09:00 Argentina Standard Time. Agenda: To consider the proposal to alter the organizational structure; to consider the election of statutory directors; and to consider the alterations in the policy of disclosing material acts or Facts and Trading of Securities.


BRF S.A., Board Meeting, May 25, 2017
Jun 7 17
BRF S.A., Board Meeting, May 25, 2017, at 12:00 Coordinated Universal Time. Agenda: To consider reference form fiscal year of 2016; to consider change in the executive board; and to consider election of member of the strategy, M&A and markets committee.


